{"tid":2398451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"給kelly看見我一個人吃吉野家","createTime":"2021-02-07T10:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T07:34:15.000Z","uid":307910,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"810f0aca6cbbb06d995c918693c8b7c662939efd","tid":2398451,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:03:59.000Z","msg":"給Kelly看見我一個人食吉野家<br />\n差點想講句好掛住你呀<br />\n但我已經懂得收斂不再說錯話<br />\n即使尷尬但不想講再見回家<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=b1c2a5ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早點看見她也可改叫外賣吧<br />\n她已和男友一同坐下<br />\n若假裝有囡囡座位要留給她<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=b1c2a5ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n講出來自己都嫌假<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=b1c2a5ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n給kelly看見我一個人食吉野家<br />\n記得童年曾與她同玩耍<br />\n天真爛漫隨意擁抱一下<br />\n我與她幾年沒見了差不多吧<br />\n今晚竟發覺有人給她一個家<br />\n<br />\n多年來踫到Kelly我亦有點怕<br />\n近況如何盡量講得不太差<br />\n給Kelly看見我一個人食吉野家<br />\n還有什麼以後可以怕<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=b1c2a5ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網"},{"pid":"91b2894d7c07f6aaf9a1aaeab4d38fa3e07c888f","tid":2398451,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"關心你精神健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df69528543e2f44b72dd0bf24109a551a1b5a24","tid":2398451,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"qu